(BAR-el-GOO-ruh) are lesser Tanar'ri resembling demonic orangutans. They are scouts and guerillas in the Blood War. 
In the Abyss, bar-lguras prefer to remain with their own kind, seldom mixing with other Abyssal natives. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planescape Monstrous Compendium, Volume 1        
              
